CVE.summary: Multiple SQL injection vulnerabilities in vehiclelistings.asp in 20/20 Auto Gallery allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary SQL commands via the (1) vehicleID, (2) categoryID_list, (3) sale_type, (4) stock_number, (5) manufacturer, (6) model, (7) vehicleID, (8) year, (9) vin, and (10) listing_price parameters.
